    When accessing the Amgen Author Collaboration website:
    * For first-time users, click this <c:Appear_AuthorEmailURLComponent URLTargetType="REMINDER" PubAuthorId="{!relatedTo.id}" ContactId="{!recipient.id}" PubId="{!relatedTo.Publication__c}"  IsAuthorComm="{!IF((relatedTo.Author__r.Profile__c=='APPEAR Portal FPR Only Submitter' && relatedTo.Author__r.Federation_Identifier__c<>NULL && relatedTo.Author__r.RecordType.Name=='Internal Contact'),'FPRS',IF(((relatedTo.Author__r.Profile__c=='Appear Portal Pub Author Login' || relatedTo.Author__r.Profile__c==NULL) && relatedTo.Author__r.Federation_Identifier__c==NULL && relatedTo.Author__r.RecordType.Name=='Appear Contact'),'AUTHOR',IF(((relatedTo.Author__r.Profile__c=='Appear Portal Pub Author Login' || relatedTo.Author__r.Profile__c==NULL) && relatedTo.Author__r.Federation_Identifier__c<>NULL && relatedTo.Author__r.RecordType.Name=='Internal Contact'),'AUTHOR',IF((relatedTo.Author__r.Profile__c==NULL && relatedTo.Author__r.Federation_Identifier__c<>NULL && relatedTo.Author__r.RecordType.Name=='Internal Contact'),'FPRS','CORE'))))}" IsMobile="false" URLTargetName="link"/> and follow as described below:
        - External Authors (not an Amgen employee): Enter the email address you want to use as your username along with a password.
        - Amgen APPEAR users will be logged into the website automatically.
            - Amgen Employees, if the link above asks for login information, please click this <a href="mailto:appearpublicationsupport@amgen.com?subject=Re:%20APPEAR%20Author%20Collaboration%20Portal%20Access%20Issue">email link</a> to send an email to the support group for login assistance.
    * Returning users, click this <c:Appear_AuthorEmailURLComponent URLTargetType="REMINDER" PubAuthorId="{!relatedTo.id}" ContactId="{!recipient.id}" PubId="{!relatedTo.Publication__c}"  IsAuthorComm="{!IF((relatedTo.Author__r.Profile__c=='APPEAR Portal FPR Only Submitter' && relatedTo.Author__r.Federation_Identifier__c<>NULL && relatedTo.Author__r.RecordType.Name=='Internal Contact'),'FPRS',IF(((relatedTo.Author__r.Profile__c=='Appear Portal Pub Author Login' || relatedTo.Author__r.Profile__c==NULL) && relatedTo.Author__r.Federation_Identifier__c==NULL && relatedTo.Author__r.RecordType.Name=='Appear Contact'),'AUTHOR',IF(((relatedTo.Author__r.Profile__c=='Appear Portal Pub Author Login' || relatedTo.Author__r.Profile__c==NULL) && relatedTo.Author__r.Federation_Identifier__c<>NULL && relatedTo.Author__r.RecordType.Name=='Internal Contact'),'AUTHOR',IF((relatedTo.Author__r.Profile__c==NULL && relatedTo.Author__r.Federation_Identifier__c<>NULL && relatedTo.Author__r.RecordType.Name=='Internal Contact'),'FPRS','CORE'))))}" IsMobile="false" URLTargetName="link"/> and follow as described below:
        - External Authors/Amgen FPR Only Submitters: Enter your username and password.
        -{!if(recipient.UserId__r.Username="","",' Username: '+recipient.UserId__r.Username)} 
        - Amgen APPEAR users will be logged into the website automatically.
    
    Best Regards,
    
    {!$User.FirstName} {!$User.LastName}
    
   If you experience a technical issue with the website, please send an email to appearpublicationsupport@amgen.com.
</messaging:plainTextEmailBody>

</messaging:emailTemplate>